Package: TwoRegression
Type: Package
Title: Process Data from Research Wearables using Two-Regression Algorithms
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person(c("Paul", "R."), "Hibbing", email = "paulhibbing@gmail.com",
		  role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Application of Various Two-Regression Algorithms for wearable
    research devices. It provides an easy way for users to read in their
    device data files and apply an appropriate two-regression algorithm
    from Hibbing et al. (2018, Med Sci Sports Exerc).
